What does Kitten say:

This is my story

Hello, my name is Kitten and I’m from a small village in Canada. My biggest goal has always been to get away from the small village one day and make something of myself, but that’s often not that easy. Times are very tough and every job is a classic time for money deal. It was often the case that at the end of the day I was so exhausted that I didn’t feel like doing anything. A friend told me about a platform where, as she puts it, you can make “quick money”. The concept was simple. You undress and people give you money for it. The sums that go over the counter here are absurdly high, so I took my iPhone, created an account and produced my first content. A few months passed and I earned my first $100 which I immediately withdrawn! This was a special moment for me as I used to earn a little more than $100 a month with a 9 to 5 job. Unfortunately, I have to admit that after half a year of work with OnlyFans I was completely exhausted and that ultimately didn’t bring in the money I had hoped for.

Just when I was about to close my OnlyFans account, I became aware of Fandafia Agency. I checked out their website and decided to make an appointment with them, which worked great. After I was signed, everything happened very quickly.

Already after the first month of cooperation I realized that I am in good hands here. I could hardly believe my eyes but in the first month I already earned 5,000 USD. And then it went steeply uphill. In the 2nd month it was already 24,000 USD, in the 3rd month 35,000 USD and after the 4 months of cooperation 57,000 USD per month.

I immediately quit my job and i am currently enjoying my time. Fandafia does so much work for me, so I only have to work 2 hours a day to maintain this high turnover. Thank you to my manager Lisa from Fandafia for always standing by my side!

- Kitten
